reviewText: Amazing i love the show just wonderful,,,,

Wonderful series, makes me feel young again just watching this.  The acting is great and each one of the characters is so believable.  This is one of my favorite shows on the TV, so now to have it to watch over again whenever I want to is a dream.

Not a single disc came up on Gracenotes with Gotham. 7 different series titles show up to select from but none Gotham. 3 discs are unreadable until I switch to a different changer. I know what talking about, I own 2,800 BR discs and 5 Sony Bluray changers that have had no issues like this before. If I can't get the last 2 discs to read I'all have to return the set...
This Blu-ray Set Is Amazing And At A Reasonable Price If You Want To Get Both Season
You can watch this in the US such a good seris
VERY ADDICTIVE.  EVERY EPISODE LEAVES YOU WANTING TO SEE THE NEXT ONE.
